       This  program  will  allow  the  user to display labels anywhere in the
       active display frame, even in areas lying outside of the  current  geo-
       graphic region.


       _d_._l_a_b_e_l  will  only  allow  the  user to type in one line of text.  The
       fully interactive program _d_._l_a_b_e_l_s can be used to  create  text  labels
       having as many as four lines.


